{
  "scriptId": "prologue_001",
  "title": "プロローグ — 潮鳴駅",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "nodeId": "start",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "——雨の匂いがした。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 1.5,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "電車が止まり、ドアが開く。\n潮風が、頬を撫でた。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 1.0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "叔母",
          "text": "蓮くん、こっちよ。久しぶりね。",
          "expression": "smile",
          "delay": 0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "叔母",
          "text": "ここでは静かに暮らしなさい。\nお母さんにはそう言われているでしょう？",
          "expression": "serious",
          "delay": 0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "「静かに」。その言葉が、胸の奥で反響する。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 0.5,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        }
      ],
      "nextNodeId": "echo_first"
    },
    {
      "nodeId": "echo_first",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "駅を出ようとした、その時——",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 1.0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "???",
          "text": "……助けて",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 0,
          "isEcho": true,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "誰もいないはずのホームから、声が聞こえた。\n振り返っても、誰もいない。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 0.8,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "……空耳だ。そう、思い込もうとした。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "（気のせいだ）",
              "nextNodeId": "ignore",
              "resonancePoints": 0,
              "requiredStat": "",
              "requiredStatLevel": 0
            },
            {
              "text": "（……今の声は）",
              "nextNodeId": "notice",
              "resonancePoints": 0,
              "requiredStat": "",
              "requiredStatLevel": 0
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "nextNodeId": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": "ignore",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "聞こえなかったことにする。\nいつもそうしてきた。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 0.5,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "でも、飲み込んだ言葉は——消えない。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 1.0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        }
      ],
      "nextNodeId": "arrive"
    },
    {
      "nodeId": "notice",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "確かに聞こえた。誰かの……声。\nでも、ホームには誰もいない。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 0.5,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "胸の奥で、何かが共鳴している。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 1.0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        }
      ],
      "nextNodeId": "arrive"
    },
    {
      "nodeId": "arrive",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speakerName": "叔母",
          "text": "蓮くん？ どうかした？",
          "expression": "worried",
          "delay": 0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "……何でもない。行こう。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "潮鳴市。\n海の見える街での、新しい日々が始まる。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 1.5,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "——これは、声を失くした少年が\n再び声を取り戻すまでの物語。",
          "expression": "",
          "delay": 2.0,
          "isEcho": false,
          "choices": []
        }
      ],
      "nextNodeId": ""
    }
  ]
}
